title: Butterbox Babies (1995) Nicholas Campbell - infant abuse
description: Oh, the nasty little corners that can be found in a supposedly free society! This is a docudrama about an orphanage which made a great noise about how charitable it was, while horrible things were happening behind its doors. The infants were given butter crates instead of cradles, quite a number were also buried thus. Instead of tut-tutting about the past, we should ask ourselves how many more abuses are going on behind our backs.
